The purpose of this project is to have a simple way of updating your Cpkg directory.
Author: ion

INSTRUCTIONS:
1) Set your working directory to wherever you want to install Cpkg
2) run the following command: 
git clone --quiet https://github.com/ion727/ConV2erter.git && bash ConV2erter/update.sh 

To update your Cpkg run the Cpkg.update.sh as a bash file (command 'bash update.sh')
